snippet.textDisplay:
Tips from virus war:
1.not go out, not go to many people's place. stay home.
2.when go out, wear the mask when entering in the elevator or your car, do not use the finger to press the button or pull the car door. should wear gloves.
3.when back home, spray alcohol to your shoes and shoes bottoms, throw your gloves
4.wash your face and hair, spray alcohol to your hand.
5.when in-home, pls use alcohol pads to rub your phones.kill virus usually.
6.pls keep warm, do not catch a cold!! because people who got a virus will seem too like being cold!
